snippet.title: Naughty Ones - Level 1 - Amiga A1200 AGA Version
snippet.description:
Level One of Naughty Ones, AGA version for the Amiga 1200. A very under-rated platform game in the mould of 'Bubble Bobble' and 'Parasol Stars'.

Game recorded using WinUAE 1.5.1 built-in recording function.
